Title: Rollin' Down in the Deeps
Description:
Got a big task for you, yes? 

Fetch things, all waxy. Bring 'em quick, yeah? Much to trade for good finds. 

Get snufflin', friend!
CompletionText: You done snufflin' yet? Got those waxy bits?
RewardText: Ah, back so soon! Show me those waxy treasures.
